Probe -> a through investigation into a crime or other matter.
Speculation -> the forming of a theory or conjecture without firm evidence.
hail -> birthplace
tamper -> interfere with (Something) in order to cause damage.
rule out -> exclude,eliminate.
levy -> impose (a tax, fee or fine).
juggling -> involving the manipulatipon of the current sense of to juggle.
Probably -> almost certainly.
Perilous -> risky, dangerous,hazardous, difficulty.
epitome -> a person or thing that is a perfect example of a particular quality or type
